they have
lost their job.

19:42.882 --> 19:46.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It can be very difficult for
those people
to afford the premiums that you
have to pay

19:46.786 --> 19:51.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
